283
00:12:20,845 --> 00:12:22,878
I really have
to go to the bathroom.

284
00:12:22,879 --> 00:12:25,080
Right here.

285
00:12:27,951 --> 00:12:31,820
37 minutes left
until the deadline.

286
00:12:31,821 --> 00:12:34,023
Someone will show.

287
00:12:34,024 --> 00:12:37,393
