00:18:06,188 --> 00:18:07,653
No problem.

406
00:18:07,655 --> 00:18:09,256
I'm really sorry about your car.

407
00:18:09,258 --> 00:18:10,556
Oh, it's all right.

408
00:18:10,558 --> 00:18:13,293
If you're free next weekend,
I'd love to take you out again.

409
00:18:13,295 --> 00:18:16,229
Um... listen,
you're a really nice guy,

410
00:18:16,230 --> 00:18:19,499
but I just... I don't think
this is working out.

411
00:18:20,367 --> 00:18:21,668
Oh. Okay.

412
00:18:21,670 --> 00:18:22,801
I'm...

